                "invention-title": [
                    "Device and method for adsorbing CO2 based on light-heat synergistic low-carbon green modified charcoal",
                    "一种基于光-热协同低碳绿色改性生物炭吸附CO2的装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a device and a method for adsorbing CO2 based on light-heat synergistic low-carbon green modified charcoal. According to the method, a modifying reagent is adopted to induce release of hydroxyl free radicals, sulfate free radicals and nitrogen-hydrogen free radicals under the synergistic effect of ultraviolet light and temperature to jointly modify the charcoal to generate high-activity sites. The modified biochar enters a mixed reaction tower and is subjected to an adsorption reaction with CO2-containing flue gas from a combustion device in the tower, the reacted biochar is separated by a cloth bag separator and then is sent into the photochemistry-thermochemistry synergistic modification tower again for modification and regeneration, and the combustion flue gas after CO2 separation is discharged into the atmosphere. According to the device and the method, the charcoal can be recycled, the gas-solid mass transfer rate of the mixed reaction tower is high, and CO2 can be efficiently adsorbed."
                },
                {
                    "p": "一种基于光‑热协同低碳绿色改性生物炭吸附CO2的装置及方法，该方法是采用改性试剂在紫外光和温度协同作用下诱导释放羟基自由基﹑硫酸根自由基﹑氮氢自由基联合改性生物炭产生高活性位点。改性后的生物炭进入混合反应塔与来自燃烧装置的含CO2烟气在塔内发生吸附反应，反应后的生物炭通过布袋分离器分离后，重新送入光化学‑热化学协同改性塔内改性再生，而分离CO2后的燃烧烟气则排入大气。该装置及方法中生物炭可循环利用、且混合反应塔气固传质速率高，能高效吸附CO2。"
                }
            ]
